let prefix = "fore" in
  let s1 = "forest" in
  print_endline (String.concat " " (List.filter (fun s -> s <> "") [string_of_bool (String.sub s1 0 (String.length prefix - 0) == prefix)]));
  let s2 = "desert" in
  print_endline (String.concat " " (List.filter (fun s -> s <> "") [string_of_bool (String.sub s2 0 (String.length prefix - 0) == prefix)]))
